relevant_findings.HEENT: Normocephalic, atraumatic, extraocular movement intact, pupils equal, round, reactive to light, no scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist, no lymphadenopathy
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, S1/S2, no murmurs/rubs/gallops
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation, no crackles or rhonchi
relevant_findings.gastrointestinal: Soft, distended, pain greater in left lower quadrant than right lower quadrant, no guarding, rebound, or peritoneal signs, positive bowel sounds in four quadrants
relevant_findings.incision/wounds: Clean, dry, intact; no hematoma or ecchymosis
relevant_findings.extremities/ms/skin: No cyanosis/clubbing/edema; feet warm, good perfusion
